{{Use British English|date=January 2014}} This article is about the [[demographics|demographic]] features of the [[population]] of the [[British Virgin Islands]], including [[population density]], [[Ethnic group|ethnicity]], education level, health of the populace, economic status, religious affiliations and various other aspects.
